	src/pic-registers.cc, src/registers.cc, src/symbol.cc, src/symbol.h,
	src/value.cc, src/value.h:
	Added command line assignments. Now you can write stuff like:
	  temp1 = temp2 << 4
	where temp1 and temp2 are two registers.

