	* src/symbol.cc: fixed gpsim crash on WIN32 in remove_module()

2004-10-13 Scott Dattalo <scott@dattalo.com>
	* src/cod.cc: Applied patch from Craig Franklin that adds support
	for reading .cod file message area.

